*rubyripper-0.5.3 (21 Sep 2008)

  21 Sep 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +rubyripper-0.5.3.ebuild:
  Version bump and use Xeconf for bug #234161.

*rubyripper-0.5.2 (07 Aug 2008)

  07 Aug 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>
  +files/rubyripper-0.5.2-require-rubygems.patch, +rubyripper-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Version bump

  21 Apr 2008; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc

  01 Apr 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> +rubyripper-0.5.0.ebuild,
  +files/rubyripper-0.5.0-editor-environment.patch,
  +files/rubyripper-0.5.0-require-rubygems.patch:
  Version bump. Adding normalize and wav useflags. Also fixing #203737.

  13 Jan 2008; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  rubyripper-0.4.4.ebuild:
  Add ruby-gettext to DEPEND too as it's used in build phase to update the
  locale files. Thanks to Patrick in bug #205602.

